title: Welcome to Jungler tryouts!
body:
Hello friends The Tilted Club is a group of four really really really good players. The sad thing is there is not five of us (tear). SO TONIGHT ON WWE SMACKDOWN WE NEED YOU!?!!!? TO TRYOUT FOR THE ROLE OF JANGLER SO WE CAN WIN THE WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP BELT.

Being serious we're a four man who cover every hole but jungle and it would be nice to turn it into a regular five man group. We range from Gold IV to Plat III. We'd prefer a Jungler who can play the top strong/meta picks (aka nidalee, graves, kindred Gragas lee etc). 

A little about us.

Starting with myself I'm the top lanes, I one trick Riv.... I mean I play tanks mainly.

Bengi from skt mid or adc plays anything but Anubis really.

Lost is a one trick Braum no other info needed.

And last and The God himself peaket fills out adc mid.

Add me in game if interested.
